OL,6,FWorkplace absences across the UK have
OL,7,Fsoared to the highest level in a
OL,8,Fdecade, a new report has found.
OL,10,FThe Chartered Institute for
OL,11,FProfessional Development (CIPD) and
OL,12,FSimplyhealth, a provider of health
OL,13,Fcash plans, are calling on businesses
OL,14,Fto create a supportive culture around
OL,15,Fhealth in the workplace.
OL,17,FIt comes after the organisations
OL,18,Fanalysed sickness absence and
OL,19,Femployee health among 918
OL,20,Forganisations, representing 6.5
OL,21,Fmillion employees.
OL,3,CUK workplace absences soar to highest
OL,4,Clevel in decade, report finds
